These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, cabbage, carrot, lettuce
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, tulip, marigold, daffodil
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, blood-red, fuchsia, azure
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, snowmobile, taxi, boat
 1. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 2. the person eating banana is in an even position##4
 3. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 5. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
 6. the person driving the car is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
 7. the person who likes blood-red is the person eating carrot##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
 9. the person driving the car is between the person driving the boat and the person who growsdaffodil##2
10. the person eating banana is the person driving the boat##1
11. the person who growsmarigold is the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | carrot  | banana    | lettuce    | cabbage   |
| Flower   | tulip     | bellflower   | marigold       | daffodil    |
| Color   | blood-red | light-blue | azure    | fuchsia |
| Transport           | snowmobile | boat       | car | taxi     |

