.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, light-blue, lilac, emerald
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, drawing, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, animation, disaster, action
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, dunhill, bongani, chaman
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
 2. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 4. the person who likes light-blue is the person watching zombie movies##1
 5. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 6. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
 7. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who likes lilac is in an odd position##4
11. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Color          | green  | light-blue    | lilac     | emerald       |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking | baking   | collecting |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | zombie   | animation   | action    |
| Cigar         | bongani | chaman  | prince | dunhill   |

