.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, mirinda, sprite
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, aconite, tulip, sunflower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, punk, funk, dubstep
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, fantasy, satire, romance
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
 2. the fan of punk is the person who growstulip##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 4. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 5. the person drinking juice is the person who growssunflower##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 7. the person watching documentary movies is the fan of dubstep##1
 8. the person who growssunflower is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
10. the person watching documentary movies is the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda   | sprite    | juice      |
| Flower           | tulip | orchid | aconite | sunflower     |
| Music-Genre   | punk      | dubstep   | ambient   | funk |
| Movie-Genre           | romance         | documentary       | satire  | fantasy       |

