.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
4 different games are played: billiard, scrabble, poker, go
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, fisherman, manager, teacher
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, sunflower, tulip, amaryllis
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, parkour, surfing
 1. the person playing billiard is the analyst##1
 2. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 3. the analyst is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 4. the person who growssunflower is in an even position##4
 5. the person playing scrabble is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 7. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the fisherman is on the left or right of the teacher##3
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who growssunflower##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
11. the person playing poker is the teacher##1
12. the teacher is on the left or right of the analyst##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Game   | go       | poker   | billiard   | scrabble   |
| Job       | fisherman        | teacher | analyst    | manager       |
| Flower      | amaryllis | sunflower    | tulip  | dahlia |
| Sport      | ice-hockey  | parkour  | cycling | surfing    |

