.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
City: hamburg, venice, rome, berlin
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, azure, red, black
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, manager, musician
There are 4 different nationalities: german, british, argentine, italian
 1. the british is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who likes red is between the german and the person traveling to berlin##2
 3. the manager is on the right of the british##1
 4. the librarian is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 5. the bartender is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 6. the person who likes blood-red is in an even position##4
 7. the person traveling to venice is the bartender##1
 8. the person who likes red is the librarian##1
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the italian##3
10. the librarian is on the right of the person who likes black##1
11. the italian is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
12. the person who likes black is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| City    | rome    | berlin      | hamburg          | venice    |
| Color   | azure | black       | red | blood-red |
| Job     | musician     | manager      | librarian     | bartender |
| Nationality   | british   | italian | argentine        | german   |

