.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, airplane, snowmobile, scooter
There 4 different types of food: apple, artichoke, cauliflower, orange
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, old-henry, aristoff, havana
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, cricket, cycling, soccer
 1. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 2. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
 3. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
 5. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
 6. the havana-smoker is between the person who's sport is cycling and the old-henry-smoker##2
 7. the aristoff-smoker is the person eating cauliflower##1
 8. the person driving the airplane is the person eating cauliflower##1
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
10. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Transport      | snowmobile  | airplane    | subway       | scooter       |
| Food          | orange    | cauliflower | artichoke | apple     |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | aristoff        | havana    | old-henry   |
| Sport   | parkour  | cycling      | soccer    | cricket |

