 2. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 3. the blend-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
 4. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 6. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 7. the owner of the goat is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
 8. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
10. the person who growsorchid is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
12. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | coffee | hot-chocolate    | soy-milk  | juice      |
| Flower   | balloon-flower      | marigold | iris | orchid   |
