The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, funk, electronic, ambient
 1. the fan of ambient is in an odd position##4
 2. the fan of blues is between the fan of ambient and the fan of electronic##2
 3. the american is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
 4. the person who growsmarigold is in an odd position##4
 5. the spanish is on the right of the nigerian##1
 6. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person eating apple##3
 7. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
 8. the person eating apple is on the left of the australian##1
 9. the fan of blues is between the american and the person who growsdaffodil##2
10. the person eating apple is on the left of the fan of blues##1
11. the person eating pear is in an even position##4
12. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
