The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, dancing, camping, woodworking
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 2. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of folk is between the owner of the mouse and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 5. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the owner of the mouse##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
10. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of house is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
13. the fan of indie is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
