 3. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person eating cauliflower is between the owner of the turtle and the person eating kiwi##2
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person eating broccoli and the person eating kiwi##2
 6. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
10. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Flower      | orchid   | rose   | poppy     | daffodil   |
| Food   | broccoli  | cauliflower       | kiwi | lettuce |
| Pet           | turtle     | goldfish   | ferret     | cat     |
| Birthday         | december | october | may   | november |

