.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, writer, freelancer, project-manager
City: colone, venice, miami, prague
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, white, yellow, fuchsia
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, sailing, volleyball, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the writer##3
 3. the person who likes green is on the left of the project-manager##1
 4. the person who likes white is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the manager##1
 6. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 7. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes yellow is on the far right##1
 9. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who likes green##1
11. the person who likes fuchsia is in an odd position##4
12. the person traveling to colone is the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Job      | freelancer       | writer | manager        | project-manager        |
| City         | prague | miami       | colone | venice |
| Color   | fuchsia     | white        | green    | yellow      |
| Sport         | sailing     | volleyball    | water-polo | badminton   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, pop, techno
4 different pets are kept: pony, frog, guinea-pig, goat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, adventure, fantasy, western
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, marigold, zinnia, rose
 1. the fan of techno is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is between the owner of the pony and the owner of the goat##2
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
 4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 5. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 6. the fan of house is the person watching adventure movies##1
 7. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
 8. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
10. the owner of the pony is in an even position##4
11. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
12. the fan of ambient is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | house      | ambient | techno     | pop        |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | goat  | frog     | pony |
| Movie-Genre         | adventure    | disaster | fantasy      | western |
| Flower     | rose | marigold     | zinnia | orchid       |

 